31[6] "Product Information. Prepopik (citric acid/Mg oxide/Na picosulfate)." Ferring Pharmaceuticals Inc, Tarrytown, NY.[7] "Product Information. Golytely (polyethylene glycol electrolyte solution)." Braintree, Braintree, MA.', 1767363023);
